Following the arrest of the former Deputy Senate President, Ike Ekwerenadu, and his wife Beatrice for alleged organ harvesting in the United Kingdom, the victim, David Ukpo has revealed his real age. The young man who alleged that he was 15 years old and was being trafficked by the Ekweremadus, told West Minister Magistrates Court on Thursday that he is 21 years old. Arise TV correspondent made this known in a live telecast
from London. Reports, however, have it that the court remanded the couple and adjourned the matter till August 4.